" How many columns of whitespace is a \t char worth?
set tabstop=4
" Referred to for “levels of indentation”, where a level of indentation is shiftwidth columns of whitespace.
set shiftwidth=4
" How much whitespace should be inserted when the tab key is pressed? And how much whitespace should be removed when the backspace key is pressed?
set softtabstop=4
" Should vim place spaces or tab upon receiving a whitespace command or a tab keypress.
set expandtab
